---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<main class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-20 sm:py-28">
			<p class="mb-4 inline-flex rounded-full border border-slate-700 bg-slate-900/70 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium tracking-wide text-slate-300">
				Stove Philosophy
			</p>
			<h1 class="max-w-3xl text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-6xl">
				Thoughtful cooking, shared simply.
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-base leading-7 text-slate-300 sm:text-lg">
				A calm place for recipes, techniques, and reflections from the kitchen. Built with Astro and styled with Tailwind CSS.
			</p>
			<div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
				<a href="#latest" class="rounded-md bg-white px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900 transition hover:bg-slate-200">
					Read latest posts
				</a>
				<a href="#about" class="rounded-md border border-slate-600 px-5 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-100 transition hover:bg-slate-800">
					About this project
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="latest" class="mx-auto grid max-w-5xl gap-5 px-6 pb-16 sm:grid-cols-3">
			<article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Technique</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Heat, then patience</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">How to build flavor with high heat and restraint instead of constant stirring.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Recipe</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">Weeknight tomato braise</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">A one-pot dinner with pantry ingredients and deep flavor in under 40 minutes.</p>
			</article>
			<article class="rounded-xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/60 p-5">
				<p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400">Notes</p>
				<h2 class="mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-white">On simple tools</h2>
				<p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-300">Why a good knife, a heavy pan, and salt can cover most of your cooking life.</p>
			</article>
		</section>

		<section id="about" class="border-y border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/40">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-14">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Built for clarity</h2>
				<p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-300 sm:text-base">
					This page uses a minimal Astro layout with Tailwind utility classes for typography, spacing, color, and responsive behavior. Use it as a foundation for your content model, blog routes, and CMS integration.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<footer class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-10 text-xs text-slate-400">
			Â© {new Date().getFullYear()} Stove Philosophy. Built with Astro + Tailwind.
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>
